From: Rafael Palomar <rafael.palomar@ous-research.no>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 20:11:13 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] COMP: Add ITK::Common to Annotations MRML link libraries

vtkMRMLAnnotationSnapshotStorageNode pulls in itksys::SystemToolsManager
via a static initialiser; without an explicit ITK::Common dependency the
symbol is undefined at link time in a standalone module build.
---
 Modules/Loadable/Annotations/MRML/CMakeLists.txt | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Modules/Loadable/Annotations/MRML/CMakeLists.txt b/Modules/Loadable/Annotations/MRML/CMakeLists.txt
index 564915bf76..944a0824ce 100644
--- a/Modules/Loadable/Annotations/MRML/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/Modules/Loadable/Annotations/MRML/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -48,6 +48,7 @@ set(${KIT}_SRCS
 
 set(${KIT}_TARGET_LIBRARIES
   ${MRML_LIBRARIES}
+  ITKCommon
   )
 
 #-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
